# Project context

ERP SaaS for procurement, inventory, sales, accounting, and CRM.

**Stack:** Laravel 13, Livewire 4, MySQL.

When implementing features, prefer deliverables in this order when applicable: migration, model, service, Livewire component. Follow service-based architecture and tenant scoping throughout.

For large tasks you may align work with roles: architect (modules, tenancy), backend (Laravel/services), frontend (Livewire), QA (flows and edge cases), refactor (performance).
